---
title: Pulled Chicken Zucchini Boats with Mozzarella and Basil
description: These zucchini boats are as easy as 1, 2, 3! A zesty tomato chicken filling comes together in no time, then load it into scooped-out zucchini and top it all with cheese. Pop it under the broiler until bubbly and crisp, and you're done!
